xmlText.p: Thomas Cook's Polish unit announces insolvency- local authorities
WARSAW, Sept 25 (Reuters) - Thomas Cook's Polish unit, Neckermann Polska, has announced that it is insolvent, local authorities told Reuters on Wednesday.
The collapse of the world's oldest travel firm Thomas Cook left hundreds of thousands of holidaymakers stranded. (Reporting by Anna Wlodarczak-Semczuk; writing by Alan Charlish)
